data.description: Check out this charming three bedroom home tucked away on over an acre lot with beautiful mature trees. Northridge school district in Saint Albans Township, this property is about 35 minutes from downtown Columbus. BRAND NEW ROOF and updated open kitchen with plenty of storage space.  Extra space in main bedroom can be converted back to a half bath with plumbing already in place. The separate garage and shed offer substantial storage as does the partial basement.  Enjoy evenings on your private patio, your front deck or just relax and enjoy country living in the large backyard with the above ground saltwater pool.  Call to schedule an appointment before it's in contract again!
